{"tid":951242,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"勞損有咩方法會可好轉除左抖下","createTime":"2018-12-22T07:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T09:55:12.000Z","uid":107520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e71b1f958d8c0e319222a73b390e4924c90ad6ed","tid":951242,"uid":107520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我老豆做左地盤好多年，年紀都有返咁上下，但仲係賺錢養家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。雖然近呢幾年都叫捱出頭，但即落啲舊患好似愈老愈痛咁，成日見佢手痛腳痛（因為佢真係唔係痛到極唔會出聲既真男人），我都好心疼，有冇巴打絲打知有咩藥或者有咩方法會令佢舒服啲？😿因爲我大學仲未畢業，都冇辦法可以賺錢養家幫輕下😭！只希望佢可以冇咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfc83b242a2739f596a8989f2bd4004bc4398c9","tid":951242,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:56:47.000Z","msg":"勞損撚路過"},{"pid":"47e629dcd696022365c9fe7aaa4dfbdbadbcfc0a","tid":951242,"uid":216694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"睇物理治療 貴都係睇"},{"pid":"b4774cbe24f2826839ba0cc2e82e1241901c01ff","tid":951242,"uid":216694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇物理治療 貴都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要</span>睇</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fd319c96436dd38703fb714e71009dbe54828ca","tid":951242,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"邊個部位勞損？"}]}